-- Emcor Group Board Elects Bershad to Replace MacInnis as Chairman
-- B y   J u s t i n   D o o m
-- 2013-06-17T19:18:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-17/emcor-group-board-elects-bershad-to-replace-macinnis-as-chairman.html
Emcor Group Inc. (EME) , the Norwalk,
Connecticut-based construction and energy infrastructure
provider, has elected Stephen W. Bershad as its chairman.  Bershad was chosen to replace Frank T. MacInnis, who had
served as chairman since April 1994, at the company’s annual
board of directors meeting on June 13, according to a filing
today. MacInnis didn’t stand for re-election.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Doom in New York at 
 jdoom1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Randall Hackley at 
 rhackley@bloomberg.net  